                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Toi, sans penser à rien, libre, tu m'attendras",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Dans ta cage : elle est neuve et solide et cachée",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "6+6",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
